            "chapterTitle": "Encouraging Livelihood by (working with) Hands and Abstaining from Begging",
            "urn": 1605360,
            "body": "<p>Abu Hurairah (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: The Prophet (\ufdfa) said, \"(Prophet) Dawud (\ufdfa) ate only out of that which he earned through his manual work.\"<br/><br/><b>[Al-Bukhari]</b>.</p>",
